when the ball flew over.

351
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,720
Chen Jing'an somehow

352
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,680
didn't catch the ball,

353
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,640
and then bam.

354
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:09,010
It hit her nose.

355
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,220
Jing'an's nose was hit?

356
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:13,410
She started bleeding.

357
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:14,370
It's Li Minqiu's fault.

358
00:19:14,510 --> 00:19:15,390
It's your fault.

359
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:17,890
I really want to slap you away
with my shoe.

360
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:19,300
Why blame me?

361
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:20,430
I didn't throw it.

362
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,220
Dad, look at Mom.

363
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:23,760
You failed to protect Jing'an.

364
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:24,970
Of course, it's your fault.

365
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:27,100
Your mom is right.

366
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:29,530
Go,

367
00:19:29,550 --> 00:19:30,760
buy some medicine,

368
00:19:32,050 --> 00:19:33,800
and apologize to Chen Jing'an.

369
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:38,010
It's already so late.

370
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,180
Are you going or not?

371
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:41,060
I'm going.

372
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,180
I don't know whose mom you are.

373
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,440
I'm going right away.

374
00:19:45,930 --> 00:19:48,510
Buy the best
and most expensive med, okay?

375
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,430
Our daughter-in-law

376
00:19:50,430 --> 00:19:51,470
can't get disfigured.

377
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:52,480
Yeah.

378
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:53,640
My wife's right.

379
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:55,640
What are you looking at?

380
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,650
What are you looking at?

381
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:58,020
Still looking?

382
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,520
Breast pain.

383
00:20:29,050 --> 00:20:30,350
What's wrong with you today?

384
00:20:33,390 --> 00:20:34,390
Just...

385
00:20:35,850 --> 00:20:37,510
Just playing basketball.

386
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:40,430
Zhu Niannian was also there.

387
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:43,550
When did you two become so close?

388
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:46,270
We...

389
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,300
We just...

390
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:52,850
She accidentally
knocked over the bikes last time,

391
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:54,680
and I spoke up for her.

392
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:57,680
Over time, we became friends.

393
00:21:00,010 --> 00:21:03,140
Niannian is really nice.

394
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:04,930
She has good grades

395
00:21:05,010 --> 00:21:06,390
and is easygoing.

396
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:09,720
If you got to know her,

397
00:21:09,930 --> 00:21:11,260
you'd definitely like her.

398
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:14,720
Not interested.

399
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:17,270
Also,

400
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,100
what's your relationship

401
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:20,390
with Li Minqiu?

402
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:22,960
Minqiu?

403
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:24,430
Minqiu?

404
00:21:26,050 --> 00:21:27,760
You've never called me like that.

405
00:21:28,890 --> 00:21:29,740
Changning.

406
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:33,270
♪Even our quarrels were always joyful♪

407
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:40,380
