410
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:53,940
♪Maybe it's better
to just end it this way♪

411
00:21:54,090 --> 00:21:56,910
♪Only after losing do I understand♪

412
00:21:56,930 --> 00:21:58,930
Don't have any contact
with Li Minqiu anymore.

413
00:21:59,430 --> 00:22:00,270
Got it?

414
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:03,140
He's obviously a punk.

415
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,470
Li Minqiu is not a punk.

416
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:08,950
- He's just...
- Chen Jing'an.

417
00:22:11,010 --> 00:22:11,850
Chen Jing'an.

418
00:22:11,850 --> 00:22:14,330
♪Beautifully bearing the bitterness♪

419
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,350
Chen Jing'an.

420
00:22:15,350 --> 00:22:20,190
♪Just act as if you never came♪

421
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,800
Chen Jing'an.

422
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:24,640
Come down.

423
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,850
I have something for you.

424
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,560
Okay.

425
00:22:45,930 --> 00:22:47,470
Don't be mad, okay?

426
00:22:49,390 --> 00:22:50,690
Have you finished your homework?

427
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,150
I just want to spend some time with you.

428
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:55,690
I don't need you

429
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,760
to keep me company.

430
00:22:58,140 --> 00:22:59,180
I'm not important.

431
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:01,550
Do whatever you want.

432
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:03,720
Do whatever you like.

433
00:23:04,100 --> 00:23:05,840
I don't have the right
to control you now.

434
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:10,550
I'm here to admit my mistake.

435
00:23:10,970 --> 00:23:12,510
I promise there won't be a next time.

436
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:15,550
From now on,
I'll do whatever you want me to do.

437
00:23:15,890 --> 00:23:17,050
Just don't be mad at me.

438
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:19,930
So, for the next monthly exam,

439
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:21,470
what rank

440
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:22,640
are you aiming for?

441
00:23:23,050 --> 00:23:24,220
I'll get whatever rank

442
00:23:24,220 --> 00:23:25,350
you want me to get.

443
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,390
Top ten in the grade.

444
00:23:31,050 --> 00:23:31,890
No problem.

445
00:23:34,140 --> 00:23:35,080
Next month,

446
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:37,430
there's also a debate contest
you must join.

447
00:23:37,430 --> 00:23:38,510
Get a ranking.

448
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,520
I'll participate.

449
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,640
Beijing is too far.

450
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:45,800
Study at a local university

451
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:46,980
and live at home.

452
00:23:47,530 --> 00:23:49,100
I'm not going to university in Beijing.

453
00:23:49,100 --> 00:23:50,140
I'll study locally.

454
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:52,600
Don't lie to me.

455
00:23:52,930 --> 00:23:53,770
My word is my bond.

456
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,500
Once said,

457
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,490
it cannot be retracted.

458
00:23:59,890 --> 00:24:01,140
(Sorry, Zhu Niannian.)

459
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:03,010
(I need to get
through this hurdle first.)

460
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:17,390
Didn't I already promise you?

461
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,390
Here.

462
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,400
This was originally

463
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:29,010
for winning

464
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:29,850
the speech contest.

465
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,550
Is it really for me?

466
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:34,760
Go and try it.

467
00:24:43,010 --> 00:24:43,970
What's this?

468
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,430
Medicine for your nose.

469
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:47,490
I didn't know which one worked best,

470
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:48,600
so I bought all of them.

471
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,600
When my mom heard you got hurt,

472
00:24:51,060 --> 00:24:52,930
she immediately asked me to see you.

473
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:54,890
I was too lazy to go upstairs.

474
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:58,180
Your mom asked you
to give me all of this?

475
00:24:58,180 --> 00:24:59,020
Right.

476
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:01,720
Does your nose still hurt?

477
00:25:02,430 --> 00:25:03,780
Not anymore.

478
00:25:05,430 --> 00:25:06,430
I don't know

479
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,760
which medicine is best.

480
00:25:07,760 --> 00:25:08,900
So, I just bought them all.

481
00:25:09,220 --> 00:25:10,100
This one is a spray.

482
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,100
It's easy to spray into your eyes.

483
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,850
(He's so nice to me.)

484
00:25:15,550 --> 00:25:17,260
Just dip a cotton ball and apply it.

485
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:32,390
This one.

486
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:33,560
This is powder.

487
00:25:33,850 --> 00:25:35,470
You need to add a little water,

488
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:36,600
but it's black

489
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:38,300
and will make you look ugly.

490
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,650
But you weren't very pretty

491
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:40,780
to start with.

492
00:25:40,890 --> 00:25:41,970
We don't care about that,

493
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:42,850
right?

494
00:25:45,420 --> 00:25:46,400
By the way, Chen Jing'an,

495
00:25:46,470 --> 00:25:48,280
what's going on
between you and Zhu Niannian?

496
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,390
Why did she suddenly

497
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:52,430
become your...?

498
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:54,930
We just became friends.

499
00:25:55,550 --> 00:25:57,010
That's great, Chen Jing'an.

500
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:59,040
I thought you just envied her,

501
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:00,000
but I didn't expect you

502
00:26:00,010 --> 00:26:01,030
to make friends with her.

503
00:26:01,990 --> 00:26:02,930
I have to admit.

504
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:05,510
You've started to look like her lately.

505
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:10,260
Really?

506
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,180
Of course. You even imitate her.

507
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:14,260
Just like this.

508
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,390
The hair flip.

509
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:17,140
No way.

510
00:26:17,390 --> 00:26:18,850
Why deny it?

511
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:19,950
Why not admit it?

512
00:26:19,970 --> 00:26:21,530
There's nothing embarrassing about that.

513
00:26:27,010 --> 00:26:27,850
Chen Jing'an.

514
00:26:54,290 --> 00:26:55,680
So sleepy.

515
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:36,140
(Oh, no.)

516
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,600
(I got caught slacking off.)

517
00:28:29,390 --> 00:28:30,510
Why does it feel like

518
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:31,800
