520
00:28:34,260 --> 00:28:37,010
It's so dark. You should go home.

521
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:39,130
Okay, I got it.

522
00:28:39,130 --> 00:28:40,380
Remember to apply the medicine.

523
00:28:40,430 --> 00:28:42,350
Say some good things later
about me to my mom.

524
00:28:42,350 --> 00:28:43,930
I didn't come all this way for nothing.

525
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:45,260
Alright, I got it.

526
00:28:45,260 --> 00:28:46,390
- Bye-bye.
- Goodbye.

527
00:30:14,100 --> 00:30:14,940
Come here.

528
00:30:18,260 --> 00:30:19,260
